comments.body:
we cannot use `encloses` because sometimes the code action range is smaller than the diagnostic range, for example:

```scala
val x = Future.successful(2)
//      ^^^^^^  diagnostic range
//       <-->   code action range
```

or even partially overlapping

```scala
val x = Future.successful(2)
//      ^^^^^^  diagnostic range
//         <------->   code action range
```

